{"tid":1434394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大學生會會長 記者會","createTime":"2019-08-08T18:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T01:11:09.000Z","uid":203739,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5bdd5ac9076db2fdb12b13dba569a3b001e6a499","tid":1434394,"uid":203739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:24:16.000Z","msg":"採訪通知：<br />\n<br />\n浸大學生會會長方仲賢交代被捕一事記者會<br />\n<br />\n八月六日傍晚，浸大學生會會長方仲賢於深水埗鴨寮街購買觀星筆後，被便衣警員截查搜身，並以「藏有攻擊性武器」之名將其拘捕達近四十八小時。<br />\n<br />\n方仲賢將就是次警方無理濫捕一事作出回應，並交代事態發展。<br />\n<br />\n 現誠邀 貴報及傳媒好友出席是次記者會。<br />\n<br />\n記者會詳情：<br />\n日期： 2019年8月9日 (星期五)<br />\n時間： 下午3點<br />\n地點： 香港浸會大學善衡校園方樹泉圖書館501室"},{"pid":"58f94b2d1bc392774432781cb786e938e59f2cd8","tid":1434394,"uid":144572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:25:23.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"769ca540e1b2d003d1d875751876f100e9e7eddd","tid":1434394,"uid":203739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:25:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"699f700bfe596203d374e351ac7e54429d2eba22","tid":1434394,"uid":203739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZiOJ645.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZiOJ645.png&h=f9742a24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27330e753dff37c4b22878ad87daf4da32aa2857","tid":1434394,"uid":179402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:27:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「幫幫手推一推」黑警唔單止搜身時恐嚇市民 仲要強光照市民對眼！ | LIHKG</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF74MRhonX28&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=9eb2b663\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOjM9aG3xZKk&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=925b683b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有乜野必要同理由對市民使用強光照住佢對眼？呢個行為有咩意義同對工作上有咩幫助？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">強烈要求黑警回應點解要用惡劣 粗暴 令人不適嘅態度 語氣 行為 去對待配合黑警工作嘅市民！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n幫手派出去 推上報<br />\n<br />\n今次拍片者冇事 下個好難講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d11cb7fad4e8018d98645d84ce54fc15d985e1","tid":1434394,"uid":242998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:36:10.000Z","msg":"其實警方肯放會長，好大可能已經在呢10支觀星筆落焊，如果他人捉到其他人用呢批筆去傷害人，會長肯定會上晒身，所以我覺得會長遲下要去警局報失，呢批筆之後嘅用途絕對唔關自己事。"},{"pid":"99a223182651710a0b05f12c85a7abeb517182bd","tid":1434394,"uid":275074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}